  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Double sabers, two-handed sword, electric arc, stick, fist, and some nameless weapons make up your arsenal, along with some outrageous hidden weapons like pistol and whip.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your enemies are all kinds of tricky flying machines, splitting, resisting multiple attacks, forming formations and spinning...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100 pieces of music with a powerful beat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Want to play your own edited music? With built-in custom track editor, you can play while editing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Free DLC is collectable content.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Includes 100 avatar skins based on dozens AAA characters, with some weapon skins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922620/extras/bc1c9e3b09a6811f547bf294413618af.avif?t=1743083922\" width=616 height=740 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Double sabers, two-handed sword, electric arc, stick, fist, and some nameless weapons make up your arsenal, along with some outrageous hidden weapons like pistol and whip.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your enemies are all kinds of tricky flying machines, splitting, resisting multiple attacks, forming formations and spinning...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100 pieces of music with a powerful beat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Want to play your own edited music? With built-in custom track editor, you can play while editing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Free DLC is collectable content.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Includes 100 avatar skins based on dozens AAA characters, with some weapon skins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922620/extras/bc1c9e3b09a6811f547bf294413618af.avif?t=1743083922\" width=616 height=740 /></span></p>",
